Modifications include:
- A-stock data layer using AKShare with multi-source fallback
- Four analyst agents (Fundamental, Technical, Sentiment, Policy)
- Bull/Bear debate with Research Manager adjudication
- Risk management debate (Aggressive/Conservative/Neutral) with Portfolio Manager
- A-stock trading constraints (T+1) in Trader
- Multi-level cache system (MD + JSON dual-write, cross-session restore)
- Agent debate trace saved to agent_cache/
- Batch analysis report generation
- Chinese language output
